=Episode 24=

3
00:00:44,119 --> 00:00:45,479
Live well.

4
00:00:47,520 --> 00:00:48,560
Use her face

5
00:00:51,600 --> 00:00:53,439
to live well.

6
00:00:53,812 --> 00:00:55,888
♪I could be with you♪

7
00:00:56,936 --> 00:00:59,359
♪Dreams are shattered, and snow spreads♪

8
00:00:59,359 --> 00:01:00,320
(Don't worry.)

9
00:01:01,280 --> 00:01:03,600
(I will definitely
fulfill our common wish.)

10
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:05,799
(Wen Yanshu,)

11
00:01:07,079 --> 00:01:09,400
(I will live well for you.)

12
00:01:38,519 --> 00:01:39,840
Who are you?

13
00:01:40,879 --> 00:01:42,120
Me?

14
00:01:43,599 --> 00:01:45,519
I'm the one who'll take your life.

15
00:01:46,519 --> 00:01:49,640
I will kill each one of you
who commits violence and brutality

16
00:01:50,680 --> 00:01:54,239
to avenge the hundreds of wronged souls
of the Lord of Zishang's Mansion.

17
00:01:55,159 --> 00:01:56,640
Including your father, the emperor.

18
00:01:58,640 --> 00:02:00,200
You're quite a big talker.

19
00:02:01,200 --> 00:02:02,200
Little girl,

20
00:02:03,359 --> 00:02:04,719
do you have the ability?

21
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:06,359
I have no way out.

22
00:02:07,159 --> 00:02:09,120
You want to kill the emperor?

23
00:02:10,800 --> 00:02:11,360
Alright.

24
00:02:12,319 --> 00:02:13,840
Maybe I can

25
00:02:14,439 --> 00:02:15,639
help you.

26
00:02:16,719 --> 00:02:17,520
What did you say?

27
00:02:18,719 --> 00:02:20,400
The emperor is your father.

28
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:23,039
His favor towards you
is known all over the world.

29
00:02:25,599 --> 00:02:26,439
Yes.

30
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:29,400
He gave me the highest status

31
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,719
and endless wealth and glory.

32
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,400
But he also gave me

33
00:02:35,439 --> 00:02:37,240
pain worse than death

34
00:02:38,639 --> 00:02:40,960
and endless torment day and night.

35
00:02:43,039 --> 00:02:43,919
Guess

36
00:02:44,840 --> 00:02:47,360
where his invulnerable blood spirit

37
00:02:48,000 --> 00:02:49,080
came from.

38
00:02:52,840 --> 00:02:55,439
It came
from sacrificing my mother's life.

39
00:02:57,000 --> 00:02:58,039
He treats me well

40
00:02:58,879 --> 00:03:01,240
only because
I can enhance his blood spirit.

41
00:03:02,199 --> 00:03:03,639
He rewards me with toyboys

42
00:03:04,520 --> 00:03:05,319
because

43
00:03:06,879 --> 00:03:08,879
I can bear a child for him.

44
00:03:09,879 --> 00:03:11,800
The day I give birth to a child

45
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:16,639
will be the day I am sacrificed.

46
00:03:26,960 --> 00:03:30,599
Brother, the blood.

47
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:35,319
We can cooperate.

48
00:03:35,879 --> 00:03:36,879
Tell me.

49
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:39,039
How do you want to take revenge?

50
00:03:52,039 --> 00:03:52,840
I want

51
00:03:54,199 --> 00:03:55,120
to become you.

52
00:04:00,439 --> 00:04:01,960
Alright, I'll let you.

53
00:04:04,639 --> 00:04:05,159
And you

54
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:08,960
need to give me freedom.

55
00:04:11,319 --> 00:04:12,400
Won't you regret it?

56
00:04:13,120 --> 00:04:15,479
I will never regret it.

57
00:04:25,824 --> 00:04:28,523
♪When the misty rain fills the world♪

58
00:04:28,921 --> 00:04:31,240
♪Wetting what I am
thinking of in my heart♪

59
00:04:31,978 --> 00:04:37,448
♪It was the year
we met under an umbrella♪

60
00:04:38,424 --> 00:04:40,811
♪Willows ride the wind,
fish play among the lotuses♪

61
00:04:41,568 --> 00:04:44,113
♪You pluck the strings of my heart♪

62
00:04:44,959 --> 00:04:45,839
(That night,)

63
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:48,800
(we exchanged appearances)

64
00:04:50,079 --> 00:04:51,720
(and disguised as each other.)

65
00:04:53,920 --> 00:04:54,519
(From then on,)

66
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,240
(I became)

67
00:04:58,639 --> 00:04:59,680
(Wen Yanshu.)

68
00:05:02,598 --> 00:05:05,745
♪Love is a curse for the sentimental♪

69
00:05:06,368 --> 00:05:08,697
♪Longing is incurable♪

70
00:05:09,244 --> 00:05:12,010
♪Better not to meet,
not to see each other♪

71
00:05:12,579 --> 00:05:14,845
♪We're not destined♪

72
00:05:15,403 --> 00:05:17,945
♪If it's to venture
the mundane world again♪

73
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:32,120
I am finally no longer Wen Yanshu.

74
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,000
You should leave.

75
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,360
But I must remind you

76
00:05:40,000 --> 00:05:42,519
