reveal our secret to the world,

77
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:45,920
I'll have no hesitation in killing you.

78
00:05:47,639 --> 00:05:48,720
Rest assured.

79
00:05:50,399 --> 00:05:51,639
From now on,

80
00:05:52,480 --> 00:05:53,920
I only want to be with my loved one

81
00:05:54,279 --> 00:05:55,480
in an isolated place

82
00:05:56,839 --> 00:05:58,000
and spend our lives together.

83
00:06:06,000 --> 00:06:07,759
I hope that someday in the future,

84
00:06:08,879 --> 00:06:10,279
a wise ruler can ascend the throne

85
00:06:11,040 --> 00:06:12,319
and bring peace to the world.

86
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:18,800
Shu,

87
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,040
what happened?

88
00:06:20,240 --> 00:06:21,040
He Chuan?

89
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:42,959
Wen...

90
00:06:49,759 --> 00:06:50,360
Shu,

91
00:06:50,600 --> 00:06:51,319
how are you?

92
00:06:56,360 --> 00:06:57,160
I am here.

93
00:06:57,399 --> 00:06:58,199
Don't be afraid.

94
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:02,040
It was close.

95
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,000
(It was close.)

96
00:07:13,360 --> 00:07:14,639
(It was so close)

97
00:07:16,079 --> 00:07:17,800
(that we could)

98
00:07:18,319 --> 00:07:19,360
(be free.)

99
00:07:37,839 --> 00:07:39,480
Your Highness, we've dismissed

100
00:07:39,839 --> 00:07:40,959
the toyboys as you ordered.

101
00:07:42,279 --> 00:07:43,120
Okay.

102
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:45,959
You can leave too.

103
00:07:48,959 --> 00:07:49,600
Your Highness,

104
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:51,399
the emperor broke his promise

105
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:52,759
and killed my sister.

106
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,120
In the past,

107
00:07:55,680 --> 00:07:56,920
to protect my sister's life,

108
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,360
my hands

109
00:07:59,879 --> 00:08:01,519
were stained with blood.

110
00:08:02,319 --> 00:08:03,040
Your Highness,

111
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:04,879
his blood spirit is weakening,

112
00:08:05,519 --> 00:08:06,399
and you have no child.

113
00:08:06,879 --> 00:08:08,079
He'll surely sacrifice you.

114
00:08:09,920 --> 00:08:10,839
Don't drive me away.

115
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:13,000
Let me stay by your side

116
00:08:13,480 --> 00:08:14,040
to guard you,

117
00:08:14,920 --> 00:08:15,560
okay?

118
00:08:16,319 --> 00:08:17,519
You want to stay by my side

119
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,319
to take revenge, right?

120
00:08:22,839 --> 00:08:24,040
Get up.

121
00:08:24,439 --> 00:08:25,279
Prepare the horses.

122
00:08:26,360 --> 00:08:27,560
Let's enter the palace.

123
00:08:28,639 --> 00:08:29,480
Yes.

124
00:08:37,360 --> 00:08:38,039
(Lord of the World, Prosperous Forever)
Your Majesty,

125
00:08:38,159 --> 00:08:39,159
Princess Royal is here.

126
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:45,840
Father.

127
00:08:49,519 --> 00:08:52,000
Father, tomorrow's
Mother's death anniversary.

128
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,919
I'll prepare a banquet at my place

129
00:08:54,120 --> 00:08:55,519
and want to invite you over.

130
00:08:57,159 --> 00:08:57,960
Shu,

131
00:08:59,399 --> 00:09:01,399
your mother has been dead
for many years.

132
00:09:01,799 --> 00:09:04,399
I am afraid you can't even remember
what she looked like.

133
00:09:05,879 --> 00:09:06,799
But

134
00:09:07,320 --> 00:09:08,960
I lost my mother at a young age.

135
00:09:09,440 --> 00:09:10,840
My mansion has long been built,

136
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,679
but you have never been there.

137
00:09:13,279 --> 00:09:14,759
My huge mansion

138
00:09:15,440 --> 00:09:16,960
is always cold and cheerless.

139
00:09:18,399 --> 00:09:19,600
I have taught you.

140
00:09:20,279 --> 00:09:21,960
You need to give up

141
00:09:21,960 --> 00:09:23,120
the sentiments

142
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:24,759
to achieve great things.

143
00:09:26,159 --> 00:09:27,600
Father,

144
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:29,240
just say yes.

145
00:09:30,039 --> 00:09:31,200
Just this once.

146
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:35,039
Look at you.

147
00:09:36,279 --> 00:09:37,080
Okay.

148
00:09:37,639 --> 00:09:38,440
Tomorrow,

149
00:09:38,960 --> 00:09:39,919
I will be there.

150
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:41,279
Thank you, Father.

151
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,080
Shadow Guard.

152
00:09:59,279 --> 00:09:59,919
Yes?

153
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,919
Take a squad of elite soldiers

154
00:10:02,279 --> 00:10:03,320
to infiltrate her mansion.

155
00:10:03,919 --> 00:10:05,440
When I am there tomorrow,

156
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,279
if there is anything unusual,

157
00:10:07,440 --> 00:10:08,480
kill without mercy.

158
00:10:08,639 --> 00:10:09,080
Understood.

159
00:10:19,080 --> 00:10:19,879
Everyone, leave.

160
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,200
Yes, Your Highness.

161
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,000
You may leave.

162
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:50,200
You can stay.

163
00:10:50,600 --> 00:10:52,360
I came here just to tell you

164
00:10:52,879 --> 00:10:53,320
my father

165
00:10:53,720 --> 00:10:55,120
is now at Yanshu's place.

166
00:11:13,879 --> 00:11:15,279
You few stay here.

167
00:11:15,799 --> 00:11:16,879
No one is allowed to enter.

168
00:11:17,080 --> 00:11:17,480
Yes.

169
00:11:33,480 --> 00:11:34,639
Tyrant,

170
00:11:35,279 --> 00:11:36,919
I can finally take your life.

171
00:11:39,360 --> 00:11:40,159
Shu,

172
00:11:42,039 --> 00:11:42,840
