at the Lord of Zishang's Mansion.

177
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:58,440
You are...

178
00:12:01,320 --> 00:12:02,399
No matter who you are,

179
00:12:03,360 --> 00:12:04,799
if you dare to kill me,

180
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:07,639
